verbose_text: The combination of the quinagolide 100 and 200 mug / day groups yielded a frequency of moderate / severe early OHSS of 10% (8/78) [P = 0.026; OR = 0.22 (0.06-0.83)]; the corresponding rate for the combination of the 50 and 100 mug / day dose levels was 13% (13/103) [P = 0.086; OR = 0.44 (0.17-1.12)].
